I"+<h3 id="the-concepts-and-build">The Concepts and Build</h3>

<p>As Speedy Wunderground had already released 3 Compilations it made sense to reference the design elements. The site was planned to launch alongside their Year 4 release, which was using black and white and the use of a 45 degree line was a constant.</p>

<p>Dan really wanted to incorporate some grainy photomontage that had also been used in some marketing.</p>

